    "1012109": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Eula",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "Here, the Gebratenes Fleisch mit Sauerkraut is ready to go! Be sure to eat it while it's hot, otherwise the flavor will be spoiled."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "And by the way, don't worry too much when Eula says strange things. She's actually a very good person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's been meaning to ask... No one could stand the sight of Eula when she was trying to speak with the others in Mondstadt earlier."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But she seemed to get along fine with you and Amber just now... what's up with that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "The people of Mondstadt don't take kindly to anyone bearing the Lawrence name."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "They are unable to see past her family, therefore they don't actually see Eula for herself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "So no matter what Eula tries to do, it's seen as a wrongdoing. It essentially strips the meaning of anything she tries to accomplish."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I think I understand now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So that's what she meant when she said it was hard for \"a bad person to try to be good.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "How come you're able to see Eula differently then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "Well, when she joined the Knights of Favonius, it caused quite an uproar."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "Many people signed a petition, demanding that the Knights reverse their decision."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "At the same time, numerous members of the Lawrence Clan crowded the entrance of the Knights of Favonius Headquarters, clamoring for Eula to give an explanation."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa... so both sides were unhappy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "That's right. So, you can imagine how determined Eula must have been under such circumstances."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "But thanks to Grand Master Varka and the unwavering attitudes of others in the Knights of Favonius, they were able to quell the unrest. Tensions still remain beneath the surface, I'm afraid."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "In the eyes of the people, she's a stain on the Knights of Favonius... and in the eyes of the Lawrence Clan, she's a disgrace to her family."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "But she simply fulfills her duty as a Knight, silently helping one person after another, myself included."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "People like Eula should be approached with care and understanding. She could stand to be treated a little more fairly."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's good that you're able to understand her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "If only there were more people like you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "I believe a day will come when things will get better."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Once everything's settled, we should go talk to Eula again. Paimon thinks we know how to communicate with her now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "I'm glad. I think that would make her very happy, though she might not ever admit it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "Take care. Please come again!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
