    "1012108": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Oh, hey Eula! I see you've met the Honorary Knight!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We meet again, Amber! Seems we're just bound to run into you these days."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Well, I just got back and was thinking about grabbing a bite at Good Hunter. But now that you're here, why don't we all eat together?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Very well. It's been some time since we've last shared a meal together."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Come, take a seat. We can discuss my uncle's gift while we eat."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "Yes, is there something else you'd like to order?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Could you please prepare a serving of my uncle's favorite, Gebratenes Fleisch mit Sauerkraut? We'll take it as a gift to him later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "Coming right up! It'll take some time to prepare, I'll have it here at the counter once it's ready."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Hold on a moment. Is this Satisfying Salad also something that Amber ordered?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "No, she didn't order it. But because she didn't order any vegetables, I thought I'd throw in a salad on the house. You know, to contrast all the meat dishes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "So... we clearly didn't order this, yet you prepared it without authorization... Hmph! Mark my words, this transgression will not go unnoticed!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh... you're going to take revenge on her for giving us a free salad!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "Hmph, you should know me by now, that's the kind of villainous character I am!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "Well then... please wait a moment while I get the dish for your uncle started."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Hmph, delicious unauthorized delicacies... Sara will pay for this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Why would you choose Gebratenes Fleisch mit Sauerkraut as a gift for your uncle? Paimon's never even heard of that dish before..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "This dish isn't actually on Good Hunter's menu. Only longstanding patrons such as my uncle would know about the dish. The old aristocrats seem to take a liking to it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Because of the sour flavor of the sauerkraut, not too many people are fond of it these days. I guess it's become less popular over time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Eula treated me to the dish once, and I couldn't even finish a bite. I've nicknamed it \"Gebratenes Fleisch mit Vengeance\" ever since. Yuck!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "I never expected us to have such completely different tastes in food... If I weren't in such a good mood, I'd say that constitutes grounds for transgression..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Huh, so even Amber doesn't escape your vengeance?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Of course not! It's hard to find someone in Mondstadt that attracts contempt as much as she does."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Haha, it's fine when you're just joking between us, but I'm afraid our Honorary Knight might misunderstand you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Eula's always talking about vengeance, but that's just how she is. It's nothing you should take too seriously."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "But I am serious! And I'll remember every transgression committed against me! Ugh, it's no wonder so many people dislike you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's starting to realize that Eula is actually a very good person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "There's no need to be so awkward when you want to say something nice."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "*sigh* Listen, you've never been labeled as a social pariah, have you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What... well... no...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "So that's why you wouldn't understand how hard it is for a bad person to try to be good. It's impossible for me, and I have no intention of acting like a good person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Alright, no need to look so sullen... I'm just kidding. Come on, let's eat. The food is getting cold."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Ooh, I'm stuffed. I'll see Sara about the bill."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "No need, I've left the Mora under the plate. If you try to settle it with her in person, she won't accept payment for the salad."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Don't underestimate my ability to exact revenge. Hah! Sara won't get the upper hand this time!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Alright, next you should pay my uncle a visit. He has a small camp at the top of the mountain near Springvale. He usually whiles his time away there when there's nothing else to do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh... Aren't you coming with us, Eula?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "I'm afraid that wouldn't be very convenient for me. It'd be better if you two went alone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Ah yes, please do remember to pick up the dish from Sara."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "I still have more recon to do in the wilderness. Well, until next time!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Let's meet again. What an interesting bunch you are."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
